params.staker: staker whose deposits are being mocked

addDeposit(address,address,uint256).notice: Adds deposit to the staker's deposits. Note that this function does not check if the staker has already deposited for the strategy.

cumulativeWithdrawalsQueued(address).notice: Mapping: staker => cumulative number of queued withdrawals they have ever initiated. only increments (doesn't decrement)

getDeposits(address).notice: Get all details on the staker's deposits and corresponding shares

setDeposits(address,address[],uint256[]).notice: mocks the return value of getDeposits

strategySharesWithdrawn(address,address).notice: Mapping staker => strategy => shares withdrawn after a withdrawal has been completed
